value.description: We need to upgrade testnet with necessary changes on genesis to include SDS testnet info. The Stratos chain need to be stopped on Oct 14, 2021 to upgrade to v0.5.0. For all testnet validator operators, please download the new genesis generated by the team and start your node again with v0.5.0, for more info, please refer to "https://github.com/stratosnet/stratos-chain-testnet/wiki/Stratos-Chain-Testnet-Validator-Upgrade-for-SDS-launch". We will not change anything from the chain state except the SDS related info. SDS will be launched after the Stratos chain upgrade is finish.
